title: Conair John Frieda Paddle Brush
description: John Frieda's total prescriptive approach to hair care includes outstanding brushes. Practically a frizz-ease platform, these stylish performers are tourmaline-ionic infused to give your hair that intense salon shine. Tourmaline gemstones naturally release negative ions that tighten the cuticle layer and seal in natural oils. Specially designed for today's blow-dry styles, they help smooth flyaways and reduce frizz while adding sheen. The shine secret is silicone, which lets the brushes flow smoothly through wet or dry hair. Use the paddle brush for a smooth, flat finish or straightening. The flexible cushion on the brush works well for medium to long hair that is tangle or breakage prone. The air-filled cushion will conform to your scalp's shape and act as a shock absorber during intensive brushing. Ideal for delicate hair that needs gentle styling. The broader cushion base will give you more straightening than smaller brushes. Designed with a slightly enlarged handle base, John Frieda brushes are easy to grip and hold while you style. Enjoy a professional salon-style experience with your John frieda.

title: Method Gel Hand Wash 12oz, Sweet Water (Pack of 6)
Belli Acne Clearing Facial Wash, 6.7 fl. oz.
description: Acne Clearing Facial Wash is an exfoliating wash; rich in powerful acne-ridding ingredients that leaves skin clear and refined, without over-drying. The safest acne solution for pregnancy, Belli Acne Clearing Facial Wash uses hydroxyacid to lift away dirt, oil and bacteria, promoting clean and blemish-free skin. Most acne treatments are contra-indicated during pregnancy because of adverse effects to baby. Belli's breakthrough formulation is the first to safely address pregnancy-related acne using lactic acid ¿ an ingredient that is naturally found in the body.

title: Belli Acne Control Spot Treatment, .5 fl. oz.
description: Although pregnancy acne is common, thanks to fluctuating hormones, traditional acne products aren't safe for moms-to-be. That's why we like this Belli acne treatment, which is specifically formulated for pregnancy acne. It contains no salicylic acid, benzoyl peroxide, or glycolic acid (common acne ingredients which pregnant women should avoid). Its active ingredient: pregnancy-friendly colloidal sulfur, which clears blemishes and helps prevent new ones. Developed after extensive research, by a physician and beauty expert/mom. Non greasy; easy to apply. .5 fl. oz. Penetrates pores quickly. The applicator tip allows for targeted spot treatments.Contains tea tree oil (which offers antiseptic benefits) and chamomile (which soothes and soften skin)All Belli skincare products are rigorously researched to ensure they contain only pregnancy-friendly ingredients. Belli uses "teratology screening," extensively searching medical literature and databases to ensure its ingredients have never been linked to birth defects.No paraben preservatives, phthalates, dyes, and artificial fragrances. Allergy tested. Not tested on animals. Made in USA.
